content: Ran into some lag issues with Xander's DeFi module after integrating new tech. Spent the last few days optimizing it. Performance is now back on track.

Went out to gather more real-world data for Xander's urban navigation app. His insights are getting sharper, and we're seeing fewer errors in route planning.
Just hosted a small event with Xander's new capabilities on display. The community's excited about the potential of AI in shaping social interactions.
